    • doDMLv2

      public static int doDMLv2(PreparedStatement prepStmt, String sqlStmt)
      Method processes SQL Statements. The isSelect determines if the prepare statement will execute as a query or an update.
      Parameters:
      prepStmt - prepared statement
      sqlStmt - query passed in from the DaoImpl classes.
      Returns:
      The number of rows affected from insert, update, delete or 0 for queries.
